        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Especially since for most people, the effects last for years and you don't have to seriously deal with hair removal.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          The human body naturally changes and regenerates continuously, so some hair may return,
          but after the initial series, 1–3 maintenance treatments per year are more than enough to keep your skin continuously smooth and inflammation-free.
